metadata.name: Brewmaster
metadata.description:
Brewmaster

This is a Brewmaster who got drunk on his own product.
tried to depict a person who lost his way with his own creations.
it really might be a self-portrait of myself, not that i am drunk, but I always sink into my thoughts and creations.
sometimes I miss sunlight.

3240x4050 Pixels. Artwork by Amirabbas Sadeghi.
